| department | salary   |
+------------+----------+
| IT         | 70000.00 |
| IT         | 72000.00 |
| IT         | 75000.00 |
| IT         | 71000.00 |
+------------+----------+
K.	Find average age by department.
mysql> select department,avg(age) from employee group by department;
+------------+----------+
| department | avg(age) |
+------------+----------+
| HR         |  37.6667 |
| Finance    |  30.5000 |
| IT         |  31.4000 |
| Marketing  |  33.6667 |
